  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1" facs= "../images/ew_g5_1757_003.jpg"/>
         <opener>
            
            <address>
               <addrLine>J.M. Sams</addrLine>            
               <addrLine><hi style="case(allcaps)">Hollywood Hotel</hi></addrLine>
               <addrLine><hi style="case(allcaps)">Dayton Roberts, Proprietor</hi></addrLine>
               <addrLine><hi style="case(allcaps)">West End - Hollywood, N.J.</hi></addrLine>
            </address>
            <address>
               <addrLine>Miss Eartha M.M. White</addrLine>
               <addrLine>221-Eagle St.</addrLine>
               <addrLine>Jacksonville</addrLine>
               <addrLine>Fla</addrLine>
            </address>
           
            <pb n="2" facs= "../images/ew_g5_1757_001.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine style="center">Hollywood Hotel</addrLine>
                  <addrLine><span style="case(allcaps)">Dayton Roberts, Proprietor</span></addrLine>
                  <addrLine><hi style="case(allcaps)">West End - Hollywood, N.J.</hi></addrLine>
               </address>
            
               <salute>
                  Dear <name type="person">Eartha</name>: <lb/> 
               </salute>
         </opener>
  
         <p>Just received a <lb/> 
            letter from Katherine telling <lb/> 
            me how ill your mother <lb/>
            is, I am real sorry to <lb/>
            hear it, and wish for <lb/>
            her recovery, give my <lb/>
            love and tell her I <lb/>
            think of her quite <lb/>
            often, and if ther is <lb/>
            any thing I can do <lb/>
            for her or you, let me <lb/>
            know and I shall <lb/>
            try to do it.  You must <lb/>
            pray for health and <lb/> </p>
         
         <pb n="3" facs= "../images/ew_g5_1757_002.jpg"/>
         
         <p>strength to keep up <lb/>
            so as to care for your <lb/>
            dear mother. With
            love and best wishes <lb/>
            for both of you <lb/> </p>
                     
         <closer> I remain your friend  <lb/>
         </closer> 
          
      </body>
  </text>
